{
  "info": {
    "name": "Issue 145 - Record Sprint Evaluation",
    "description": "Manual verification flow for Issue 145 (POST /sprint-evaluations, GET /sprint-evaluations/{evaluationId}). Run the authentication requests first so JWTs are captured automatically. The collection uses the rubric fixture IDs from the backend implementation and the real schedule endpoint to open/close the SPRINT window. Before running the happy path, make sure {{advisorOwnedGroupId}} is assigned to professor@example.com and stays aligned with the fixture groupId used by the sprint evaluation service. If you want to validate the ownership-violation case, set {{unownedExistingGroupId}} to a real group that exists but is not assigned to professor@example.com.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
